Package: mfrmr
Type: Package
Title: Flexible Many-Facet Rasch Model Estimation Without FACETS
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Ryuya", family = "Komuro", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "ryuya.komuro.c4@tohoku.ac.jp")
Author: Ryuya Komuro [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Ryuya Komuro <ryuya.komuro.c4@tohoku.ac.jp>
Description: Flexible many-facet Rasch model (MFRM) estimation and diagnostics
    using a native R implementation. Supports arbitrary facet counts, RSM/PCM,
    MML/JML estimation, FACETS-style bias iteration, fixed-width report output,
    APA text generation, and visual warning summaries.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
