    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    tibble,
    purrr,
    stringr,
    gt,
    plotly,
    psych,
    rlang,
    stats,
    utils
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
